            </p>
            @*<p><a class="btn btn-default">Get started &raquo;</a></p>*@
        </div>
    </div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h3>The little things...</h3>
        <p>
            How do you capture life's little everyday moments? Do you need reminded to take a picture with a friend or family member? Do you want to record a story or a song? Never forget a moment with the help of Stemma.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default">Get started &raquo;</a></p>
