        <h3>The big things...</h3>
        <p>Record all of those major life-changing moments - weddings, graduations, births, a new job, and buying a house - what changed in your life and what changed you. Keep track of it all with Stemma.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default">Get started &raquo;</a></p>
        @*<input type="submit" value="Get started" &raquo; class="btn btn-default" />*@
